任律師提起上訴者，應一併繳納上訴審裁判費。\r\n中    華    民    國    109   年   12     月    30    日\r\n                              書記官  王人俊","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/KLDV/109%2c%e5%9f%ba%e7%b0%a1%2c1070%2c20201230%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"KLDV,109,基簡,1070,20201230,1","JYEAR":"109","JCASE":"基簡","JNO":"1070","JDATE":"20201230","JTITLE":"清償債務"}